a": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c7298a6987a3c338ae77006a91867644_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "441 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/536280435"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIx/zs85T354YlEAMaCDgxNDU1MjMwIIjS9ZQGMAg4owFABHIJNTM2MjgwNDM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1654531883.6623118", "card_id": "Q_32004546", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 300}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么很多网游玩家对「自动寻路」嗤之以鼻？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我发现有不少玩家甚至把不玩自动寻路游戏当成了原则。可是我玩网游，剑三 FF14 和古剑这种没自动寻路的，我要做任务要找人就只能死死盯着地图，剑三任务有尖头指引还好点，另外两款我玩了几天视线都在地图上，升级路上根本没空看风景。 这两天玩了一下天刀，发现有自动寻路，想起之前的龙之谷也有，在自动寻路的路上我可以左右移动镜头欣赏路上的风景，我觉得这是很好的设计，可为什么那么多玩家把自动寻路当成毒瘤一样看待？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-eff750180c92aa5a2764a986fd33f2d3_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "375 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/32004546"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0Ix/zs85T354YlEAMaBzUwMDExODIguIjwrAUwGjjACEAFcggzMjAwNDU0NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1654531883.6629546", "card_id": "Q_353434853", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 352}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "西安是否如网上所说「工资低，高消费」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如果是，造成这种现状的原因是什么？目前的西安和北上广比起来哪里更适合就业？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-280c7596ba0f272b0d020677b4a8e656_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "304 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/353434853"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ix/zs85T354YlEAMaCDQwODE5MDE5IPTv6u0FMCc4sQdABnIJMzUzNDM0ODUzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1654531883.6635504", "card_id": "Q_535889585", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "俄罗斯突然出手，限制包括氖在内的惰性气体的出口，此举对全球芯片行业有何影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中国基金报记者 王建蔷自新冠肺炎疫情爆发以来，世界范围内持续出现史无前例的缺芯潮，「芯」慌笼罩全球。而如今，全球缺芯危机或将更加严重。俄罗斯根据批准的政府法令限制了包括氖在内的惰性气体的出口。这些气体包括氩气、氦气和其他气体是被用于生产半导体不可缺少的原材料俄罗斯突然出手：限制出口！芯片行业又慌了？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-70ca7655ddf46e5c0770daa21f2489ae_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "248 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/535889585"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIx/zs85T354YlEAMaCDgxMzY4NDQ4INGj5pQGMAM46AFAB3IJNTM1ODg5NTg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1654531883.6642702", "card_id": "Q_520528313", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 238}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "轿车为什么不把外壳设计成跑车的样子，这样可以卖得更贵吧？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "即使没有跑车的性能，就不能设计类似跑车的外形来满足部分人的虚荣心理吗？为什么轿车不能用跑车的外壳？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-8b40014133e46fe21c1700642e43b608_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "234 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/520528313"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIx/zs85T354YlEAMaCDc3OTU0NjQwIPCUlpEGMB04gAdACHIJNTIwNTI4MzEzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1654531883.6649063", "card_id": "Q_536250718", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1759}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "高考倒计时 1 天，让我们把最好的祝福传递给高考生，你有什么话想对他们说？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://p